uickly becomes difficult and requires an active mindset. Holopoint is designed so that only a few determined archers will reach the last wave.\n\nWARNING: THIS GAME GETS INTENSE. REMEMBER TO BREATHE AND TAKE BREAKS.", "short_description": "Holopoint is pure archery madness. Fight your way through waves of responsive targets, samurai, and highly dangerous ninjas - all while drawing, nocking, and shooting your arrows as quickly as possible."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.alzanstudios.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Alzan Studios, LLC", "support_website_url": "https://www.alzanstudios.com/contact", "website_url": "http://www.alzanstudios.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_FEW", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "3744040075834813"}, {"id": "1592192974313489"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "ARCADE", "SPORTS"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "242358471386267"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 8, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "3866884890225269"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "330227858401075"}, {"status": "PENDING", "id": "1992016621182522"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "483350939399094"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "706543204704469"}, {"status": "PENDING", "id": "1295693981824515"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "549058256244600"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "687832922645464"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "3866884890225269"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nod